title: Tooltips for player
body:
Feature requested in #263

Added tooltips for the player buttons, artist, album and song in the player area.

The tooltips are only in English and French, other languages use English text. Using Google Translate seems a bad idea as there could be different meanings for the same text. Help will be appreciated if anyone could help translating before or after the merge :)
